data.description: VA loan assumption at 2.25% for qualified buyers and 2nd lien position ok. Stunning townhouse with prime location close to I-75, Cityplace, Knox Henderson, and Lower Greenville. Recently updated with LVP floors and fresh coat of interior and exterior paint. All lightbulbs are LED for lower electricity bills. Private fenced backyard with turf and zero-scaped landscaping has little to no maintenance and is perfect for pets. High 9' and 10' ceilings, large bedrooms, 2nd floor is perfect for entertaining with 2 living areas, dining room and open kitchen. 2 car attached garage and plenty of street parking if needed. 4th bedroom on bottom floor with separate entrance is perfect for office, additional bedroom, or income-producing Airbnb. Lots of new builds in neighborhood, but very few are this large and 4 bed is very rare...great value! No HOA.
